    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:justify; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.18; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">夹具设置步骤将在本部分进行说明。使用此夹具夹紧/松开顺序</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">可以</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">进行</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">设置，</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">联锁</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">可以</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">进行</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">设置</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;"> &#160;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;"> 堆栈之间</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">和</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">还可以监控</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;"> 夹具</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">的状态</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; letter-spacing:-1px;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">。</text></para>
